dient en="unrefined cane sugar" commodity="Q57656231">zcucker</ingredient> dar vff gesewet das smecket woil so die <ingredient en="garden pea" commodity="Q29472543">erbis</ingredient> nit versaltzen sin </div></body></text></TEI>